      <title>美联储处于等待模式。投资者希望放心，如果需要，它将采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/fed-meeting-this-week-has-investors-anxiously-awaiting-powell-s-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）在本周面临棘手的任务，因为这两项任务都可以确保投资者的经济保持坚实的地位，同时还可以传达决策者准备就绪，如有必要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/fed-meeting-this-week-has-investors-anxiously-awaiting-powell-s-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 18:59:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持续不必担心市场，呼吁更正健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）是前对冲基金经理，他说，由于美国试图重塑其经济政策，他并不担心最近的经济下滑，从股票市场擦掉了数万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-16/bessent-says-he-s-not-worried-about-market-corrections-healthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 15:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巨大的美国风暴产生龙卷风，野火，至少有32人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-16/tornadoes-wildfires-and-blinding-dust-sweep-across-u-s-as-massive-storm-leaves-at-least-32-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰勒敦（Tylertown），密西西比州（AP）＆Mdash;多个美国各州的异常恶毒和破坏性的天气产生了剧烈的龙卷风，蒙蔽了沙尘暴和快速移动的野火，至少有37人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-16/tornadoes-wildfires-and-blinding-dust-sweep-across-u-s-as-massive-storm-leaves-at-least-32-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2025 05:46:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
